title: Was a U.S. Border Patrol Officer Killed by Attackers Armed with Rocks?
subtitle: Questions remain about the November 2017 death of U.S. Border Patrol Officer Rogelio Martinez, but little evidence suggests he was killed by rock-wielding attackers.
author: Dan Evon
vclaim: A U.S. border patrol agent was killed by attackers using rocks near the border of the United States and Mexico.
